Text.Page: My hammer is for the echelon of the Iron Order.
The federation is crumbling. We built this hall for those who will stand strong.

At the request of the exarch, I currently offer silver quality enchanting. My silver enchanting is more successful than my bronze. If you want an even higher standard, ask your exarch to change it to gold.
